snippet.title: My Femboy Roommate [Demo] DOWNLOAD WINDOWS/ANDROID/MAC
snippet.description:
My Femboy Roommate Demo Version Download Windows Linux Android Apk Mac iOS Web - RenPy Adult Visual Novel Games by Nuteku #myfemboyroommate 

About This Game:
In My Femboy Roommate, you've just moved to a new city and are looking for a quiet place to launch your indie dev career. You share an apartment with your new roommate, Robin. He is a shy but cute livestreamer who reveals himself to be a Femboy. Do you have what it takes to form a genuine relationship with your new Femboy roommate?

This is a demo version of the game and currently includes the first 8,000 words of content, or roughly 15-20% of the full game. Things are a work-in-progress and will be updated and improved based on YOUR feedback. 

The game is currently available to wishlist on Steam

Release Date: 2024-08-22
Developer: Nuteku - https://discord.gg/3sBCbHMUDZ | https://www.patreon.com/Nutekuu
Censored: No
Version: Demo
OS: Windows, Linux, Mac, Android, Web
Language: English, Spanish, Russian, German, Japanese, Turkish, Chinese (Simplified & Traditional), Portuguese, Korean, French, Czech, Dutch, Hindi, Italian, Polish, Thai, Vietnamese
Other Games: https://youtu.be/0nV9SbqWYnA

Notes:
This game is a demo version of the full game. It is still being developed, so things are subject to change and may be unfinished.

Most sprites and scenes in the game have been made using handmade drafts of poses (ControlNet) and reworked by an artist for consistency. The voice-work has also been enhanced and transformed using tools that utilize artificial intelligence, but are not the work of any text-to-speech AI. Translations in languages other than English are also done with the assistance of AI models and revised for accuracy. No Live-Generated AI content is used.
